        <mxCell id="8" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px&quot;&gt;Occasional Drug Use&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;b&gt;Definition:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The use of alcohol/psychoactive substances to ‘have fun’,usually in social settings. (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.emcdda.europa.eu/system/files/publications/211/Dif06en_63529.pdf&quot;&gt;EMCDDA, 2002&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Description:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;curiosity, testing out, semi-regular use, socialising aspects e.g. partying&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=ext;double=1;rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;shadow=0;spacing=5;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="240" y="206" width="160" height="404" as="geometry" />
